pan><br />\n<br />\n迫晒你地去金鐘做自己覺得承受唔到同無成效既事又點？前線都一定會出現矛盾，大家做自己覺得有用同承受到風險既事，槍頭向外，先叫和而不同<br />\n<br />\n同而不和既係 黑警 建制 政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"06ed6c8762a782d894506e3360d0436745d80f23","tid":1213672,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8fcaff4ba94df1f76b453711219fea42e40a6a","tid":1213672,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"我地同黑警唔同既係我地有思考，識自己判斷應該做點樣既事，所以應該互相支持 條條大路通羅馬<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係黑警，黑警無思考，叫佢去金鐘用棍用槍就一定要聽，"},{"pid":"5b1d9fc103654b1b50e8a97371a2089c7bf78b11","tid":1213672,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfa0f05e8eedd0cc26045e5952b7b891d8801cf","tid":1213672,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e6ccde0eaae6d8b1a9d9d9073cec42e3ec3b3aa","tid":1213672,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a33d8d4b5a20d09d893cab19bebda7c467ca7191","tid":1213672,"uid":47659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"367c5931c8a26995a7a27868e62507a215091005","tid":1213672,"uid":237562,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n好多人唔敢上前線<br />\n但係咪真係冇用呢?<br />\n一隊軍隊都唔係得先鋒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"我只想肯定各自付出 不要分化 <br />\n利申612有份屌柒佢地唔好塞紅線 因為真係影響前線野餐人手"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"同你意見一樣<br />\n之前我都反612個日搞港鐵 會阻礙支援<br />\n但今日就正好時機<br />\n尋日班狗太癲 開槍殺人<br />\n今日一定佈好曬陣準備大屠殺<br />\n加上好多人都身心俱疲 人數少 天氣差 不宜硬碰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:45:56.000Z","msg":"唔想挫前線士氣，只係客觀分析今日如果又all in衝擊一定效率